# Vendor Federation

Vendor information may be shared across APP federation networks.

Federation allows:

* Cross-domain vendor verification
* Shared reputation signals
* Shared security alerts
* Shared revocation events

No central registry is required.

---

# Vendor Endorsements

Organizations may issue endorsements.

Examples:

```text
Enterprise Approved
Verified Partner
Certified Vendor
Trusted Supplier
Preferred Provider
```

Endorsements are represented through Attestations.

---

# Vendor Revocation

Vendor records may be revoked.

Reasons include:

* Domain compromise
* Fraud
* Security incidents
* Legal violations
* Federation violations

Revocations should be visible to all federation participants.

---

# Vendor Categories

Vendors may advertise categories.

Example:

```json
{
  "categories": [
    "ai",
    "cloud",
    "payments"
  ]
}
```

Categories assist procurement agents in discovery.

